<section sectnbr = "1D">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "04">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A1406027" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Rastavljanje i ponovo sastavljanje ventila i glave motora
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A1406026">Uklanjanje i ugradnja ventila i glave motora</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A1406027001">
<title>
Rastavljanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite venturi priključak (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141070.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "64.914mm" ver = "01" gw = "140" gh = "167"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Redom poslažite rastavljene dijelove osim brtve stabla ventila i vodilice ventila tako da ih možete postaviti na njihovo mjesto.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Radi lakšeg servisiranja glave motora, odvojite od nje brizgaljke i ispušnu granu.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pomoću specijalnih alata (A) i (B) potisnite oprugu ventila, a zatim odvojite konusne čahure ventila (1) također specijalnim alatom (C).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D017">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-14510">
09916-14510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D018">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-14522">
09916-14522
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D019">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-84511">
09916-84511
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140093.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "104.340mm" ver = "01" gw = "159" gh = "279"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Oslobodite specijalne alate (podizač ventila) i uklonite držač opruge i oprugu ventila.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Izvadite ventil sa strane komore za sagorijevanje.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odvojite brtvu stabla ventila (1) i sjedište opruge ventila (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140094.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.000mm" ver = "01" gw = "161" gh = "128"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pomoću specijalnog alata uklonite vodilicu ventila sa strane komore za sagorijevanje do strane opruge ventila.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D020">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-44310">
09916-44310
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140095.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.873mm" ver = "01" gw = "150" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A1406027002">
<title>
Ponovno sastavljanje
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A1406028">Pregled ventila i vodilica ventila</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A1406029">Provjera glave motora</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A1406031">Pregled opruge ventila</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Prije postavljanja vodilice ventila na glavu motora, razvrtite otvor vodilice s specijalnim alatom (10,5 mm razvrtačem) da biste uklonili nepravilnosti i učinili ga okruglim.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D021">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-34542">
09916-34542
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D022">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-37320">
09916-37320
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140096.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.990mm" ver = "01" gw = "198" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Specijalnim alatom ugradite novu vodilicu ventila na glavu motora kako slijedi.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D023">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-57330">
09916-57330
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D024">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-56011">
09916-56011
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Ne koristite rabljenu vodilicu ventila. Postavite novu vodilicu ventila veću od standardne.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vodilice ventila za usis i ispuh su jednake.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Jednolično zagrijte glavu motora na temperaturu između 80 i 100 &#176;C (176 do 212 &#176;F) tako da se glava ne iskrivi, a zatim specijalnim alatima utisnite novu vodilicu ventila u otvor vodilice.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Novu vodilicu ventila utiskujte dok specijalni alat ne dođe u dodir s glavom motora.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Nakon postavljanja, uvjerite se da vodilica ventila viri iz glave motora propisanom dimenzijom &#34;a&#34;.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<spec>
<title>
Izbočina vodilice ventila (unut. i vanj.)
</title>
<ptxt>
“a”: 11,0 – 11,5 mm (0,4331 – 0,4528 in)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140097.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "65.986mm" ver = "01" gw = "185" gh = "170"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Razvrtite provrt vodilice ventila specijalnim alatom.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Očistite strugotine s otvora.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D025">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-34542">
09916-34542
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D026">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-34570">
09916-34570
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140096.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.990mm" ver = "01" gw = "198" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite sjedište opruge ventila na glavu motora.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite novu brtvu stabla ventila (1) na vodilicu ventila.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Nakon nanošenja motornog ulja na brtvu stabla ventila i osovinu specijalnog alata (B), nataknite brtvu stabla ventila na osovinu, a zatim postavite brtvu stabla ventila na vodilicu ventila tako da rukom potisnete specijalni alat.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Nakon ugradnje provjerite da je brtva stabla ventila ispravno učvršćena na vodilicu ventila.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Prilikom ugradnje ne udarajte specijalni alat čekićem ili nečim sličnim. Postavite brtvu stabla ventila na vodilicu tako da rukom gurate specijalni alat. Kuckanje ili udaranje specijalnog alata može uzrokovati oštećenja na brtvi stabla.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D027">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09917-98221">
09917-98221
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D028">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-57330">
09916-57330
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140098.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "74.834mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "195"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nanesite motorno ulje na brtvu stabla ventila, provrt vodilice ventila i stablo ventila.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite ventil na vodilicu ventila.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140099.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.990mm" ver = "01" gw = "178" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite oprugu ventila i držač opruge.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Svaka opruga ventila ima gornji kraj (široki završetak (1)) i donji kraj (uski završetak (2)). Svakako oprugu postavite donjim krajem (uskim završetkom) prema dnu (na sjedište opruge ventila).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "36.940mm" ver = "01" gw = "60" gh = "88"/>
<callout>
